  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the role:</strong><br /><br />Commerce.sg is a performance marketing and content production company. <br /><br />We are looking for a <strong>Marketing & Operations Executive</strong> to support our team with day-to-day marketing, project coordination and basic people management.<br /><br />You’ll get exposure to clients, creators and partners, and learn how a fast-moving marketing company runs. </p><p><strong>Key responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Help plan and execute marketing campaigns and content calendars <br />(mainly TikTok & IG).</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with producers, editors and designers to make sure campaigns and assets are delivered on time.</p></li><li><p>Track basic performance numbers and prepare simple updates or reports.</p></li><li><p>Maintain project trackers, follow up on deadlines and help improve SOPs and workflows.</p></li><li><p>Support intern and junior staff management: assigning tasks, checking progress, helping with onboarding.</p></li><li><p>Join meetings with clients/partners where needed and follow up on action items.</p></li><li><p>Any other duties assigned by the Director to support smooth marketing and business operations.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What we’re looking for</strong></p><ul><li><p>Candidates with strong interest in digital marketing, social media and business operations.</p></li><li><p>Hungry to learn, take ownership and grow into a bigger role over time.</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with basic spreadsheets and organising information.</p></li><li><p>Confident communicator, comfortable dealing with different people <br />(internal team, interns, clients).</p></li><li><p>Organised, dependable, and able to handle a fast-paced, changing environment.</p></li></ul>",
